fy_concreteyard

Finding a thin line between fy_ and aim_ maps.
A map with a fightyard feel is less dependent on reflexes, but more upon tactics, teamwork and aim.
Optimized using nodraw textures
104 weapon spawns total
48 weapon spawns on each side - 4 of each:

m3
mac10
tmp
ump45
mp5navy
p90
galil
famas
ak47
m4a1
sg552
aug

4 scouts on towers
4 m249s on walls

48 terrorist spawns
48 counter-terrorist spawns


  Created by MNtMzng
  Beta-tested by Goatslapper and others

This is my first map that I have put on FPSB, so you could give me some slack, please?
